The code that this exception references is:
https://github.com/elastic/elasticsearch/blob/5.5/core/src/main/java/org/elasticsearch/search/aggregations/bucket/BestBucketsDeferringCollector.java#L160

Which has a comment that we do not expected the scorer to ever be null here.

Although this bug was found on 5.5 and I have not been able to reproduce it yet I suspect it might still exist on recent versions as on master we make the same assumption:
https://github.com/elastic/elasticsearch/blob/master/server/src/main/java/org/elasticsearch/search/aggregations/bucket/BestBucketsDeferringCollector.java#L168

